title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Aug 13 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Aug 13 2022
description:
DOJ source to Newsweek on Trump raid: "spectacular backfire." Trump outsmarted the FBI by breaking the story himself. Rand Paul: Garland impeachment on table over Trump raid. Senator Ron Johnson joins C&B to react to the Mar-a-Lago raid, his Senate contest. Clay and Buck thank listeners for support. Kash Patel told us in May that Trump declassified large volumes of deep state documents.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
